lead_paragraph: Scott Hend of Australia and Felipe Aguilar of Chile made it through blustery conditions and shot 3-under 69 to share the lead Thursday after the first round of the Aberdeen Asset Management Scottish Open.

headline.print_headline: Hend, Aguilar Shoot 3-Under 69 for Lead at Castle Stuart
